#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:24
msgid ""
"Once all desired settings have been enabled, click the :guilabel:`Save` "
"button in the upper-left corner of the :guilabel:`Settings` page."
msgstr ""
"После включения всех необходимых настроек нажмите "
